                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-148" type="surname" value="NALDER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-148" type="given" value="HOWARD"></interp>HOWARD NALDER</persName>
                  </hi>. I took the prisoner from Lingham. He gave me this piece out of his hat—he denied having it at first.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner pleaded poverty, and received a good character.)</p>
